```bash
sudo ./motion_detector
```

Make sure the HC-SR501 PIR sensor is connected to GPIO4 and the buzzer is connected to GPIO18 before running the program. The program will log each motion event (timestamp and duration of buzzer activation) to the 'motion_log.txt' file.

