    init_wiringPi();

    while (1) {
        if (read_touch_sensor()) {
            toggle_relay();
        }
        usleep(DEBOUNCE_DELAY * 1000); // Debounce delay in microseconds
    }

    return 0;
}
```

Compile the program using gcc:

```
gcc relay_control.c -o relay_control -lwiringPi
```

Finally, run the compiled program:

```
sudo ./relay_control
```

